    <tr><td class="text-center">5–7</td><td class="text-center">65%</td><td class="text-center">84%</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="text-center">8–9</td><td class="text-center">50%</td><td class="text-center">76%</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="text-center">10–11</td><td class="text-center">35%</td><td class="text-center">68%</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="text-center">12–14</td><td class="text-center">20%</td><td class="text-center">60%</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="text-center">15+</td><td class="text-center">1%</td><td class="text-center">25%</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<hr>

<h4>Catapult Attack</h4>
<p>
  Catapults (1 per Town Center) can be sent on special missions. Choose a target type:
</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Army &amp; Towers</strong> — destroy enemy military units and towers</li>
  <li><strong>Population</strong> — kill enemy civilians</li>
  <li><strong>Buildings</strong> — demolish enemy buildings</li>
</ul>
<p>
  Only catapults can defend against incoming catapult attacks.
  Catapult attack and defense points: <%= @soldiers['catapult']&.attack_points&.to_i || 25 %> / <%= @soldiers['catapult']&.defense_points&.to_i || 25 %>.
</p>

<hr>

<h4>Thief Attack</h4>
<p>
  Thieves (1 per Town Center) can be sent on covert operations. Available missions:
</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Steal Army Info</strong> — learn the exact army composition of the target</li>
  <li><strong>Steal Building Info</strong> — learn the exact building counts of the target</li>
  <li><strong>Steal Research Info</strong> — learn the research levels of the target</li>
  <li><strong>Steal Goods</strong> — steal a portion of the target's resources</li>
  <li><strong>Poison Water</strong> — kill a portion of the target's population and army</li>
  <li><strong>Set Fire</strong> — demolish some of the target's buildings</li>
</ul>
<p>
  Only thieves defend against thief attacks.
  Thief attack / defense: <%= @soldiers['thieve']&.attack_points&.to_i || 50 %> / <%= @soldiers['thieve']&.defense_points&.to_i || 55 %>.
</p>

<hr>

<h4>Battle Mechanics</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Attack outcome has a random ±10% swing.</li>
  <li>Wall protection adds a percentage bonus to defender's defense points.</li>
  <li><em>Military Losses</em> research reduces casualties (up to 50% reduction at 50 levels).</li>
  <li><em>Attack Points</em> research increases your attack power by 1% per level.</li>
  <li><em>Defense Points</em> research increases your defense power by 1% per level.</li>
  <li>Soldiers starving during a campaign survive at 95% rate per turn of starvation.</li>
</ul>
